海外疫情紧张，在外中国人如何回国？韩国来华航班为何爆满？中国是否会对疫情高风险国家人员采取限制措施？3月1日，国务院联防联控机制召开新闻发布会，就如何有效防控海外疫情输入的相关问题，给出权威回答。
On March 1, the Joint Prevention and Control Mechanism of the State Council held a press conference to give authoritative answers on how to effectively prevent and control the import of overseas epidemic diseases.
发布会现场全国治愈出院比例达52.1%国家卫生健康委新闻发言人、宣传司副司长米锋：除湖北以外，其他省份新增确诊病例3例，连续3天保持个位数，新增疑似病例68例，新增死亡病例1例，重症病例减少36例。
In addition to Hubei province, three new cases were confirmed, the number of cases remained in single digits for three consecutive days, 68 new cases of suspected cases, 1 case of new death and 36 cases of serious cases were reported.
近一周，武汉、湖北和全国确诊病例治愈率均持续上升，全国治愈出院比例达到52.1%，说明全国疫情防控总体形势持续向好，医疗救治效果明显，救治压力正在减轻。
Over the past week, the cure rate of confirmed cases in Wuhan, Hubei and the whole country has been on the rise, with 52.1 percent of patients cured nationwide.
旅居疫情严重国家的中国人如何回国？外交部领事司司长崔爱民：在目前确诊病例较多的韩国、日本、意大利和伊朗等国，有不少的华侨和留学生等人员，中国政府高度关注他们在当地的健康安全。
How do Chinese who live in countries with severe epidemics return home? Cui Aimin, director of the Consular Department of the Ministry of Foreign Affairs: In countries such as South Korea, Japan, Italy and Iran, where there are many confirmed cases, there are quite a few overseas Chinese and foreign students, and the Chinese Government is highly concerned about their health and safety there.
目前，疫情比较严重的国家还没有完全断绝与外界的公共交通，我们在当地的人员可以选择以直航或者是中转绕道的方式回国。
At present, the more serious countries have not completely cut off public transport with the outside world, our local personnel can choose to return by direct flights or by way of detours.
若疫情进一步发展，我在当地人员的健康安全受到严重威胁，我们将采取必要措施，积极协助和安排他们回国。
If the outbreak develops further and the health and safety of my personnel on the ground are seriously threatened, we will take the necessary measures to actively assist and arrange their return.
对外国入境人员如何采取防控措施？外交部领事司司长崔爱民：根据疫情发展情况，中国地方政府将及时动态调整对外国来华人员入境后的防控措施，我们对外国公民和本国公民一视同仁，无差别地执行相应措施，并且会充分照顾当事人的合理关切，尊重他们的宗教和风俗习惯。
In the light of the development of the epidemic situation, Chinese local governments will adjust the measures for the prevention and control of the entry of foreign nationals into China in a timely and dynamic manner. We will treat foreign nationals and Chinese citizens alike, implement corresponding measures without discrimination, and will fully accommodate the legitimate concerns of the parties and respect their religions and customs.
入境后，他们所在的社区还将为他们提供必要的保障和协助，帮助他们解决好生活方面的实际困难。
Upon arrival, their communities will also provide them with the necessary guarantees and assistance to help them cope with the practical difficulties of living.
当前，中国的防疫工作已经进入最吃劲的关键时期，我们希望疫情严重国家的人员，在来华时能够充分理解并积极配合中方的相关防控举措，共同防范好疫情相关风险，维护好自己和他人的健康安全。
At present, China's epidemic prevention work has entered a crucial and demanding period, and we hope that people from countries with severe epidemics will fully understand and actively cooperate with China's relevant prevention and control measures when they come to China, work together to prevent the risks associated with the epidemic, and safeguard their health and safety and that of others.
所有出入境人员都必须进行健康申报海关总署卫生检疫司司长林伟：要求所有出入境人员都必须进行健康申报。
All persons entering or leaving the country are required to submit a health declaration. Secretary for Health and Quarantine of the General Administration of Customs Lin Wei: All persons entering or leaving the country are required to submit health declarations.
海关对所有出入境人员严格实施“三查、三排、一转运”措施。
The Customs strictly enforces the "three checks, three rows and one transhipment" measures for all entry and exit personnel.
“三查”：100%查验健康申报，全面开展体温监测筛查，严密实施医学巡查；“三排”：对“三查”中发现有症状的，或是来自于疫情比较严重的国家或地区，或是接触过确诊病例、疑似病例的人员，严格实施流行病学排查、医学排查以及实验室检测进行排查；“一转运”：对“三排”当中判定的确诊病例、疑似病例、有症状人员、密切接触者四类人员，一律按照有关规定，采取转运、隔离、留观等防控措施。
"Three check": 100% check health declaration, complete temperature monitoring screening, strict implementation of medical inspection; "three row": "three check" found symptoms, or from the more serious cases of the disease, or contact with confirmed cases, laboratory tests, strict implementation of epidemiological, medical and laboratory tests, "a trans-shipment:
目前中外人员交流秩序总体较通畅外交部领事司司长崔爱民：前一段时间，一些国家对于中国公民入境采取了不同程度的管控措施，大部分国家的有关做法都是出于维护本国和外国公民的健康安全及维护地区与国际卫生公共安全，有关举措是比较专业的、科学的，也是恰当的。
Recently, some countries have adopted different measures to control the entry of Chinese citizens into their territory. Most of them have adopted measures to protect the health and safety of their own and foreign citizens and to safeguard regional and international public health and safety.
对此，我们予以理解和尊重。
We understand and respect that.
但也有个别国家反应过度，采取了一些不必要的措施，对此我们也进行了必要交涉。
But there have also been individual countries that have overreacted by taking unnecessary measures, and we have made the necessary representations.
目前看，中外人员交流的秩序总体上还是比较通畅的，没有太大的障碍。
At present, the order of communication between Chinese and foreign personnel is relatively smooth in general, and there are not too many obstacles.
先后派出10架次航班接回1314名中国公民外交部领事司司长崔爱民：疫情发生以来，外交部和中国驻外使领馆认真细致扎实地做好每一项具体工作，驻外使领馆的领事服务工作一直在正常开展。
Since the outbreak of the outbreak, the Ministry of Foreign Affairs and Chinese embassies and consulates abroad have done every specific job conscientiously and solidly. Consular services at embassies and consulates abroad have been operating normally.
疫情发生以来，协调国内有关航空公司，先后派出10架次的航班前往多个国家，接回了1314名中国公民。
Since the outbreak of the outbreak, China has coordinated domestic airlines, sent 10 flights to various countries and retrieved 1,314 Chinese citizens.
同时，还积极协助特区政府，从日本接回了钻石公主号上的近200名港澳特区居民。
At the same time, the SAR Government has been actively assisting the SAR Government to retrieve nearly 200 Hong Kong and Macao SAR residents from Japan.
中国与日韩间航班数减少中国民用航空局飞行标准司司长朱涛：近期，韩国、日本疫情发展迅速，中外航空公司减少了部分航班。
China, Japan and South Korea to reduce the number of flights China Civil Aviation Administration Director Zhu Tao: South Korea, Japan, the recent rapid development of the epidemic, Chinese and foreign airlines have reduced some of the flights.
本周中韩间航班总量已降至320班，预计下周将进一步减至276班；中日间航班总量下降至380班，预计下周进一步减至263班。
The total number of inter-Korean flights has dropped to 320 this week and is expected to further reduce to 276 next week, and the total number of mid-day flights to 380 is expected to further reduce to 263 next week.
韩国来华航班爆满？机票紧张所致国家移民管理局边防检查管理司司长刘海涛：从2月23日到现在，韩国公民来华入境数量日均是1300人，航班满座的情况是因为航班数量减少导致机票紧张。
South Korea Flights Flooded to China Liu Haitao, head of the border inspection and management department at the National Immigration Administration, said: From February 23 to the present, the number of South Korean citizens arriving in China is 1,300 a day.
从韩国来华人数有小幅增加，没有大的波动。
There has been a small increase in the number of people arriving from South Korea without major fluctuations.
从近期自韩国入境人员的成分看，主要以中国的内地居民为主，占到约七成。
Judging by the composition of recent arrivals from South Korea, the majority of them are mainland Chinese residents, accounting for about 70%.
目前没发现大量韩国人涌入我国的情况。
There has been no significant influx of South Koreans into the country.
Play来源：中新视频　　疫情期间在华外国人停居留期限到后自动顺延2个月国家移民管理局边防检查管理司司长刘海涛：疫情防控期间，‍‍在华的外国人如果停居留期限已经到了，‍‍可以自动顺延两个月，‍‍顺延的期限内，‍‍没有必要再去办理‍‍延期手续，‍‍仍可以在华合法的停居留或者‍‍正常的出境。
During the period of epidemic prevention and control, foreign nationals living in China can stop their stay automatically for two months. If the stay period for foreign nationals in China comes to an end, they can automatically delay their stay for up to two months.
Play来源：中新视频来源：中国新闻网推荐阅读点击大图|富士康最难最贵“复工季”：北上广深部分中介获得返费高达17000元点击大图|出生45天婴儿确诊！韩专家称最坏情况是40%国民感染,，疫情或至年底！。
Foxconn's toughest and most expensive "get back to work season": Some brokers in northbound Shenzhen have been paid as much as $17,000 for a 45-day baby diagnosis! Korean experts say the worst-case scenario is 40% national infections, or by the end of the year.
